<div
  style="
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto,
      Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #374151;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 40px auto 0 auto;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  "
>
  <!-- Logo -->
  <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
    <img
      src="https://i.imgur.com/y1jxH6X.png"
      alt="Logo"
      style="max-width: 300px; height: auto; margin: 30px auto 0 auto;"
    />
  </div>

  <h1 style="margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.3; color: #374151;">
    Reservation Confirmation
  </h1>

  <div style="text-align: left; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 16px;">
    <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">
      Dear <%= @first_name %> <%= @last_name %>,
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
      Thank you for your reservation! We are thrilled to have the opportunity to host you and your guests. Our team is committed to making your dining experience memorable, and we look forward to serving you with the finest dishes and impeccable service on your special day.
    </p>

    <h2
      style="
        margin-top: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        line-height: 1.25;
        color: #f15623;
      "
    >
      Reservation Details
    </h2>

    <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
      <li><strong>Reservation Date:</strong> <%= @reservation_date %></li>
      <li><strong>Meal Period:</strong> <%= @meal_period %></li>
      <li><strong>Number of Guests:</strong> <%= @number_of_guest %></li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @email %></li>
      <li><strong>Mobile Number:</strong> <%= @mobile_number %></li>
      <li>
        <strong>Price:</strong>
        <%= number_to_currency(@price, unit: "₱", precision: 0, delimiter: ",") %>
      </li>
      <% if @downpayment.present? && @downpayment > 0 %>
        <li>
          <strong>Payment:</strong>
          <%= number_to_currency(@downpayment, unit: "₱", precision: 0, delimiter: ",") %>
        </li>
      <% else %>
        <li><strong>Payment:</strong> Full Payment</li>
      <% end %>
      <li>
        <strong>Total:</strong>
        <%= number_to_currency(@total, unit: "₱", precision: 0, delimiter: ",") %>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2
      style="
        margin-top: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        line-height: 1.25;
        color: #f15623;
      "
    >
      Courses Selected
    </h2>

    <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
      <li>First Course: <strong><%= @first_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Second Course: <strong><%= @second_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Third Course: <strong><%= @third_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Fourth Course: <strong><%= @fourth_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Fifth Course: <strong><%= @fifth_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Sixth Course: <strong><%= @sixth_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Seventh Course: <strong><%= @seventh_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Eighth Course: <strong><%= @eighth_course %></strong></li>
      <li>Ninth Course: <strong><%= @ninth_course %></strong></li>
    </ul>

    <p style="margin: 16px 0;">
      If you have any questions or need to make changes to your reservation, please contact us at inquiries@mesaprivado.com
      or call 0917-560-5069.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 16px 0;">
      If you want to cancel your reservation, please click the button below:
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; text-align: center;">
      <a
        href="<%= "#{ENV['FRONTEND_URL']}/cancel/#{@cancellation_token}" %>"
        style="
          display: inline-block;
          background-color: #f15623;
          color: #ffffff;
          text-decoration: none;
          padding: 12px 24px;
          border-radius: 12px;
          font-weight: bold;
          text-align: center;
        "
      >
        Cancel Reservation
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 16px 0;">
      Note that cancellations must be made at least 7 days before the reservation date.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 0;">Best regards,</p>
    <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Mesa Privado Team</strong></p>
  </div>
</div>
